Package classOrderPacking

Class Container

java.lang.Object
classOrderPacking.Box
classOrderPacking.Container
All Implemented Interfaces:
order.packing.IBox, order.packing.IContainer
public class Container
extends Box
implements order.packing.IContainer
Class of Container It extends the class of Box and implements the interface of Container It has the properties of Box, plus a reference, a color, a color edge and an array of items
